snippet.title: 2Dark - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
2Dark is coming to PS4, Xbox One and PC on March 17, 2017

From Frédérick Raynal, the creator of Alone in the Dark and famed pioneer of survival-horror games, 2Dark is a grim journey of stealth and courage into the heart of corruption...

Buy it from Amazon: http://amzn.to/2lJkEqB
